        <p>*Kpn, <italic>Klebsiella pneumoniae</italic>; Eco J529, <italic>Escherichia coli</italic> transconjugant strain; Eco J53, recipient <italic>E. coli</italic> J53; ND, not determined.&#x2028;&#x2020;PCR screening included <italic>bla</italic><sub>TEM</sub>, <italic>bla</italic><sub>SHV</sub>, <italic>bla</italic><sub>OXA-1</sub>-like, <italic>bla</italic><sub>CTX-M</sub> groups 1, 2, and 9, <italic>bla</italic><sub>VEB</sub>, <italic>bla</italic><sub>PER</sub>, <italic>bla</italic><sub>GES</sub>, <italic>bla</italic><sub>OXA-48</sub>-like, <italic>bla</italic><sub>IMP</sub>, <italic>bla</italic><sub>VIM</sub>, <italic>bla</italic><sub>KPC</sub>, <italic>bla</italic><sub>NDM-1</sub>, and 6 groups of <italic>bla</italic><sub>AmpC</sub> genes.</p>
